custom_sql:
select pay_date::date as ds
    ,  seller_region as region
    , sum(items_price) as y 
from dma.tv_current_order_full_mini cof 
join dma.current_microcategories using(microcat_id) 
where create_date::date >= '2018-07-01' 
and subcategory_id in (47, 18, 5, 11, 16, 57,22,60,37,52)
and pay_date is not null
and seller_region not in ('Владимирская область','Калужская область', 'Нижегородская область', 'Ростовская область',  'Самарская область','Свердловская область', 'Тверская область','Тульская область','Ярославская область')
group by 1,2

custom_sql:
select  
csc.eventdate::date as ds ,
            case 
                when Region in ('Ростовская область','Нижегородская область','Воронежская область',
                'Волгоградская область','Оренбургская область')
                then 'target' 
                else region end as region,
        count(distinct hash(Event_Date::date, logical_category_id, Cookie_id)) as y
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc  
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id) 
join DMA.users_home_location_segment l on participant_id = user_id and l.event_date = csc.eventdate::date  
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = l.home_city_id 
where EventDate::date >= '2019-01-01'::date 
and csc.user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest) 
and split_part(cm.logical_category, '.', 1) = 'Transport'
and Platform_id = 3
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

custom_sql:
with users_logcats as (
    select ci.user_id, 
        ci.item_id,
        cm.logical_category_id, 
        ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
        ci.location_id,
        row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
    from DMA.current_item ci 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
    where vertical = 'General'
        and logical_category = 'General.Electronics'
        and subcategory_name = 'Телефоны'
        and cm.param1 not in ('Аксессуары','Рации','Стационарные телефоны')
        and (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
        and ci.StartTime >= '20190101'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    (case when 'Москва,Московская область,Санкт-Петербург,Ленинградская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target'
           else region end) as region, 
    count(distinct user_id) as y
from users_logcats ld
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = ld.location_id
where rnk = 1 
    and event_date >= '20190101'
    and country = 'все регионы'
    and region not in ('Татарстан','Красноярский край','Кемеровская область','Иркутская область','Хабаровский край','Пензенская область',
                        'Ярославская область','Ульяновская область','Томская область','Калининградская область','Ивановская область','Бурятия','Карелия','Ямало-Ненецкий АО',
                        'Ханты-Мансийский АО','Оренбургская область', 'Волгоградская область','Удмуртия','Чувашия','Новосибирская область','Тюменская область','Кировская область',
                        'Свердловская область', 'Нижегородская область')
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

custom_sql:
select urm.event_date::date as dt,
        (case when 'Москва,Московская область,Санкт-Петербург,Ленинградская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target'
           else region end) as region,
        sum(case when product_type in ('lf','vas','subscription','cpa') then urm.transaction_amount_net_adj end) as y
    from DMA.user_report_metrics urm  
    left join DMA.current_transaction_type ctt 
        using(TransactionType_id)    
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm 
        using(microcat_id)
    join DMA.current_locations cl 
        using(location_id)
    where event_date >= '20190101'
        and vertical = 'General' 
        and logical_category = 'General.Electronics'
        and subcategory_name = 'Телефоны'
        and cm.param1 not in ('Аксессуары','Рации','Стационарные телефоны')
        and country = 'все регионы'
        and region not in ('Татарстан','Красноярский край','Кемеровская область','Иркутская область','Хабаровский край','Пензенская область',
                        'Ярославская область','Ульяновская область','Томская область','Калининградская область','Ивановская область','Бурятия','Карелия','Ямало-Ненецкий АО',
                        'Ханты-Мансийский АО','Оренбургская область', 'Волгоградская область','Удмуртия','Чувашия','Новосибирская область','Тюменская область','Кировская область',
                        'Свердловская область', 'Нижегородская область')
    group by 1,2
    order by 1,2

Астраханская область,Иркутская область,Калининградская область,Рязанская область,Ставропольский край
custom_sql:
SELECT event_date as ds ,
       case when clp.locationname in ('Астраханская область','Иркутская область','Калининградская область','Рязанская область','Ставропольский край') then 'target'
            else clp.locationname end as region ,
       sum(metric_value) as y
FROM   dma.regional_ab_metrics ab join dma.current_locations cl using (location_id) join dma.current_locations clp
        ON cl.parentlocation_id = clp.location_id
WHERE  user_segment_market = 'any'
   and is_user_asd = 'any'
   and cl.isactive
   and platform_id = 3
   and event_date >= date_trunc('year', timestampadd(year,-3, current_timestamp))::date
   and vertical_id in (SELECT DISTINCT vertical_id
                    FROM   dma.current_microcategories
                    WHERE  vertical = 'Realty')
   and logical_category_id = -1
   and metric_name = 'buyers'
   and ab.location_id not in (SELECT location_id
                           FROM   dma.current_locations
                           WHERE  isactive
                              and (parentlocation_id in (SELECT parentlocation_id
                                                      FROM   dma.current_locations
                                                      WHERE  locationname in ('Астраханская область','Иркутская область','Калининградская область','Рязанская область','Ставропольский край'))
                              and parentlocation_id != 2885))
   and clp.locationname not in ('все регионы', 'Москва','Санкт-Петербург','Москва')
GROUP BY 1, 2

custom_sql:
select  EventDate::date as ds
        , case when 'Татарстан,Ивановская область,Калужская область,Нижегородская область,Хабаровский край,Кемеровская область,Ханты-Мансийский АО,Волгоградская область,Воронежская область,Орловская область,Курганская область,Рязанская область,Тверская область,Алтайский край,Костромская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target' 
            else cl.region        end as region
        , count(distinct Cookie_id) as y        
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc 
join DMA.current_item ci on csc.Item_id = ci.Item_id 
join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = ci.microcat_id
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = ci.location_id
where EventDate::date >= '20200101' and cm.Param1 = 'Готовые строения и срубы'
        and ('Татарстан,Ивановская область,Калужская область,Нижегородская область,Хабаровский край,Кемеровская область,Ханты-Мансийский АО,Волгоградская область,Воронежская область,Орловская область,Курганская область,Рязанская область,Тверская область,Алтайский край,Костромская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%'
            or 'Новосибирская область,Ставропольский край,Тульская область,Владимирская область,Ярославская область,Архангельская область,Ульяновская область,Северная Осетия,Марий Эл,Хакасия' like '%'||cl.region||'%')
        and country = 'все регионы'
    group by 1,2

custom_sql:
select EventDate::date as ds
, (case when 'Иркутская область,Кемеровская область,Ямало-Ненецкий АО' like '%'||cl.region||'%' 
    or 'Екатеринбург,Нижнекамск' like '%'||cl.City||'%' then 'target'
    when 'Тюменская область,Красноярский край,Новосибирская область,Воронежская область,Костромская область,Амурская область,Брянская область,Ростовская область,Томская область,Еврейская АО,Крым' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then region 
    else city end) as region
, count(distinct csc.Cookie_id) as y
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
join DMA.current_locations cl using(location_id)
join DMA.buyer_birthday bb on bb.Cookie_id = csc.Cookie_id and bb.first_contact_event_date = csc.EventDate
where EventDate::date >= '20190101'
and (vertical = 'General'  or vertical = 'SpareParts') 
and logical_category = 'General.Furniture'
and country = 'все регионы'
and (('Иркутская область,Кемеровская область,Ростовская область,Ямало-Ненецкий АО,Томская область,Еврейская АО,Новосибирская область,Воронежская область,Костромская область,Амурская область,Брянская область,Красноярский край,Тюменская область,Крым') like '%'||cl.region||'%'
    or ('Киров,,Уфа,Улан-Удэ,Комсомольск-на-Амуре,Нижнекамск,Екатеринбург') like '%'||cl.City||'%' )
and item_id not in (select item_id from dma.current_item where isDead)
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

custom_sql:
SELECT event_time::date as ds ,
       case when clp.locationname in ('Астраханская область','Иркутская область','Калининградская область','Рязанская область','Ставропольский край') then 'target'
            else clp.locationname end as region ,
       count(installed_at) as y
FROM   dma.adjust_installs ai join dma.current_locations cl using (location_id) join dma.current_locations clp
        ON cl.parentlocation_id = clp.location_id
WHERE true
   and event_time::date >= date_trunc('year', timestampadd(year,-3, current_timestamp))::date
   and ai.location_id not in (SELECT location_id
                           FROM   dma.current_locations
                           WHERE  isactive
                              and (parentlocation_id in (SELECT parentlocation_id
                                                      FROM   dma.current_locations
                                                      WHERE  locationname in ('Астраханская область','Иркутская область','Калининградская область','Рязанская область','Ставропольский край'))
                              and parentlocation_id != 2885))
   and clp.locationname not in ('все регионы', 'Москва','Санкт-Петербург','Москва')
GROUP BY 1, 2

custom_sql:
select  EventDate::date as ds
        , case when 'Новосибирская область,Ставропольский край,Тульская область,Владимирская область,Ярославская область,Архангельская область,Ульяновская область,Северная Осетия,Марий Эл,Хакасия' not like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target' 
            else cl.region        end as region
        , count(distinct Cookie_id) as y        
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc 
join DMA.current_item ci on csc.Item_id = ci.Item_id 
join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = ci.microcat_id
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = ci.location_id
where EventDate::date >= '20200101' and cm.Param1 = 'Готовые строения и срубы'
        and country = 'все регионы'
        and Region not in ('Санкт-Петербург и Ленинградская область','Москва и Московская область') 
        and Region != 'Undefined'
    group by 1,2

    EventDate::date as ds,
    (case when cl.region = 'Ставропольский край'
        then 'target' else region end) as region,
    count(distinct Cookie_id) as y        
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
    join DMA.current_locations cl using(location_id)

    and EventDate::date >= '20190101' 
    and logical_category in ('General.Fashion')
    and country = 'все регионы' -- 'Россия'

order by 1,2

    and loc.event_date > '20230301'
    and vertical = 'General'
    and logical_category = 'General.Fashion'
    and user_location_id in (22,346,992,1294,1344,3771,3976,4145)
)

custom_sql:
with items as
(
    select Item_id, region       
    from DMA.current_item sie 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = sie.microcat_id 
    join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = sie.location_id -- в gmv_deals_proxy не нашла Location_id поэтому оставила current_item
    where  StartTime::date >= '20190101'
            and logical_category = 'General.ConstructionRenovation'
            and country = 'все регионы'
            and region not in ('Нижегородска область', 'Москва', 'Московская область', 'Санкт-Петербург', 'Ленинградская область')
            and not isDead
            and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    (case when region = 'Татарстан' then 'target' else region end) as region,
    sum(proxy_deals) as y 
from DMA.gmv_deals_proxy dp 
join items using (item_id)
where  event_date::date >= '20190101'
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

with users_logcats as (
    select ci.user_id, 
        ci.item_id,
        cm.logical_category_id, 
        ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
        ci.location_id,
        row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
    from DMA.current_item ci 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
    where (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
        and ci.StartTime >= '20190101'
        and vertical = 'Services'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    'target' as region, 
    count(distinct user_id) as y
from users_logcats ld
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = ld.location_id
where rnk = 1 
    and event_date >= '20190101'
    and country = 'все регионы'
group by 1

        , (case when 'Краснодарский край,Свердловская область,Ростовская область,Башкортостан,Тюменская область,Челябинская область,Нижегородская область,Самарская область,Ставропольский край,Новосибирская область,Пермский край,Воронежская область,Омская область,Тверская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target'

    , case when 'Свердловская область,Кемеровская область,Воронежская область,Чеченская Республика,Владимирская область,Вологодская область,Саха (Якутия),Смоленская область,Северная Осетия,Псковская область,Ингушетия,Ненецкий АО' like '%'||cl.region ||'%' then 'target'

custom_sql:
select  create_date::date as ds
    , case when 'Татарстан,Дагестан,Иркутская область,Хабаровский край,Калининградская область,Тамбовская область,Коми,Мурманская область,Кабардино-Балкария,Хакасия,Костромская область' like '%'||cl.region ||'%' then 'target' 
        else cl.region        end as region
    , count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y        
from dma.current_order  co
join DMA.current_order_item
    using(deliveryorder_id)
join dma.current_microcategories cm
    using(microcat_id)
join dma.current_locations cl 
    on  co.buyer_location_id = cl.location_id
where     true
    and 'Челябинская область,Нижегородская область,Алтайский край,Приморский край,Ярославская область,Кировская область,Липецкая область,Рязанская область,Ивановская область,Амурская область,Карачаево-Черкесия,Магаданская область,Свердловская область,Кемеровская область,Воронежская область,Чеченская Республика,Владимирская область,Вологодская область,Саха (Якутия),Смоленская область,Северная Осетия,Псковская область,Ингушетия,Ненецкий АО,Башкортостан,Красноярский край,Саратовская область,Ханты-Мансийский АО,Чувашия,Пензенская область,Калужская область,Мордовия,Ямало-Ненецкий АО,Новгородская область,Сахалинская область,Чукотский АО,Самарская область,Ставропольский край,Омская область,Оренбургская область,Тюменская область,Тверская область,Архангельская область,Забайкальский край,Бурятия,Курганская область,Камчатский край,Тыва,Москва,Санкт-Петербург,Московская область,Краснодарский край,Ростовская область,Волгоградская область,Крым,Ленинградская область,Белгородская область,Курская область,Брянская область,Астраханская область,Орловская область,Адыгея,Калмыкия' not like '%'||cl.region||'%' 
    and create_date > current_date - 366*4
    and pay_date is not null
    and vertical = 'General'
group by 1,2

custom_sql:
with users_logcats as (
    select ci.user_id, 
        ci.item_id,
        cm.logical_category_id, 
        ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
        ci.location_id,
        row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
    from DMA.current_item ci 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
    where true 
        and vertical = 'SpareParts'
        -- and vertical = 'General'
        and (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
        and ci.StartTime >= '20190101'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    (case when city = 'Владивосток' then 'target' else region end) as region, 
    count(distinct user_id) as y
from users_logcats ld
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = ld.location_id
where rnk = 1 
    and event_date >= '20190101'
    and country = 'все регионы'
    and (city = 'Владивосток' 
            or region not in ('Бурятия', 'Саха (Якутия)', 'Забайкальский край', 'Камчатский край', 'Приморский край', 'Хабаровский край', 
                            'Амурская область', 'Магаданская область', 'Сахалинская область', 'Еврейская АО', 'Чукотский АО'))
group by 1,2

custom_sql:
select EventDate::date as ds
, (case when 'Архангельская область,Чувашия,Владимирская область,Белгородская область,Удмуртия,Оренбургская область,Мурманская область,Смоленская область,Ивановская область,Пермский край' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target'
        when 'Тюменская область,Красноярский край,Новосибирская область,Воронежская область,Костромская область,Амурская область,Брянская область,Ростовская область,Томская область,Еврейская АО,Крым' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then region
        else city end) as region
, count(distinct csc.Cookie_id) as y
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
join DMA.current_locations cl using(location_id)
where EventDate::date >= '20190101'
and (vertical = 'General'  or vertical = 'SpareParts')
and cm.Param1 = 'Женская одежда'
and country = 'все регионы'
and (('Тюменская область,Красноярский край,Новосибирская область,Воронежская область,Костромская область,Амурская область,Брянская область,Ростовская область,Томская область,Еврейская АО,Архангельская область,Чувашия,Владимирская область,Белгородская область,Удмуртия,Оренбургская область,Мурманская область,Смоленская область,Ивановская область,Пермский край,Крым') like '%'||cl.region||'%'
    or ('Киров,,Уфа,Улан-Удэ,Комсомольск-на-Амуре') like '%'||cl.City||'%' )
and item_id not in (select item_id from dma.current_item where isDead)
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

with users_logcats as (
    select ci.user_id, 
        ci.item_id,
        ci.isDeliveryActive,
        cm.logical_category, 
        cm.logical_category_id, 
        ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
        row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
    from DMA.current_item ci 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
    where vertical in ('General', 'SpareParts')
        and (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
        and ci.StartTime >= '20160101'
),
user_segments as 
(
    select event_date, 
        ld.user_id, 
        ld.rnk, 
        ld.logical_category_id,
        ld.item_id,
        ld.isDeliveryActive,
        max(nvl(usm.segment_rank, ls.segment_rank)) over(partition by ld.user_id, ld.logical_category_id) as max_user_segment_rank
    from users_logcats ld
    left join dma.user_segment_market usm
           on usm.user_id = ld.user_id
          and usm.logical_category_id = ld.logical_category_id
          and usm.converting_date interpolate previous value ld.event_date
    -- в справочнике есть дефолтный сегмент для каждой логической категории
    left join dict.segmentation_ranks ls on ls.logical_category_id = ld.logical_category_id and ls.is_default
    where event_date >= '20170101'
        and ld.logical_category = 'General.Hobby'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    'target' as region, 
    sum(new_listers_with_delivery)/sum(new_listers) as y
from 
    (
    select event_date,
        count(distinct hash(user_segments.user_id, logical_category_id)) as new_listers,
        count(distinct case when isDeliveryActive = True then item_id end) as new_listers_with_delivery
    from user_segments
    where rnk = 1 
        and max_user_segment_rank = 101
    group by 1 
    ) t
group by 1 
order by 1
limit 50000

select   StartTime::date as ds,
        'target' as region,
        count(distinct Item_id) as y        
from DMA.current_item sie 
join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = sie.microcat_id
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = sie.location_id
where  StartTime::date >= '20190101'
        and country = 'все регионы'
        and vertical = 'Services'
    group by 1
order by 1

custom_sql:
select 
    event_time::date as ds, 
    case when Region in ('Свердловская область','Ростовская область','Самарская область','Новосибирская область','Башкортостан','Московская область','Алтайский край','Кемеровская область','Тюменская область','Приморский край','Забайкальский край','Пермский край','Кировская область','Тверская область','Хабаровский край','Оренбургская область','Ханты-Мансийский АО','Чувашия','Чеченская Республика','Владимирская область','Белгородская область','Рязанская область','Мурманская область','Курская область','Ленинградская область','Смоленская область','Бурятия','Курганская область','Амурская область','Кабардино-Балкария','Костромская область','Саха (Якутия)','Марий Эл','Мордовия','Ямало-Ненецкий АО','Сахалинская область','Калмыкия','Республика Алтай','Магаданская область','Еврейская АО','Чукотский АО') 
then 'target' else Region end as region,
    count(distinct adjust_cookie_id) as y 
from dma.adjust_installs id
inner join dma.current_locations cl on id.location_id = cl.location_id 
and event_time::date > '2019-09-01' 
and Region not in ('Москва', 'Санкт-Петербург')
and adjust_event_type = 'install'
and adjust_platform = 'android'
group by 1,2 order by 1,2

target_location: Владимирская область,Калужская область, Нижегородская область, Ростовская область,  Самарская область,Свердловская область, Тверская область,Тульская область,Ярославская область
custom_sql:
select purt.event_date as ds
    , case when 'Владимирская область,Калужская область, Нижегородская область, Ростовская область,  Самарская область,Свердловская область, Тверская область,Тульская область,Ярославская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target' 
        else cl.region end as region
    ,sum(purt.transaction_amount_net_adj) as y
from dma.v_paying_user_report_full purt 
left join dma.current_locations cl using(location_id) 
where purt.event_date::date >= '2018-07-01' 
and is_revenue = true and is_classified = true 
and subcategory in ('Книги и журналы', 'Коллекционирование') 
group by 1,2

control_locations: Ростовская область,Томская область,Еврейская АО,Киров,Новосибирская область,Воронежская область,Костромская область,Амурская область,Брянская область,Крым,Уфа,Улан-Удэ,Красноярский край,Комсомольск-на-Амуре,Тюменская область
custom_sql:
select EventDate::date as ds
, (case when 'Иркутская область,Кемеровская область,Ямало-Ненецкий АО' like '%'||cl.region||'%' 
    or 'Екатеринбург,Нижнекамск' like '%'||cl.City||'%' then 'target'
    when 'Тюменская область,Красноярский край,Новосибирская область,Воронежская область,Костромская область,Амурская область,Брянская область,Ростовская область,Томская область,Еврейская АО,Крым' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then region 
    else city end) as region
, count(distinct csc.Cookie_id) as y
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
join DMA.current_locations cl using(location_id)
where EventDate::date >= '20190101'
and (vertical = 'General'  or vertical = 'SpareParts')
and cm.Param1 = 'Женская одежда'
and country = 'все регионы'

custom_sql:
with items as
(
    select Item_id, region       
    from DMA.current_item sie 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = sie.microcat_id 
    join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = sie.location_id -- в gmv_deals_proxy не нашла Location_id поэтому оставила current_item
    join DMA.user_segment_market using(user_id)
    where  StartTime::date >= '20190101'
            and logical_category = 'General.ConstructionRenovation'
            and country = 'все регионы'
            and region not in ('Нижегородска область', 'Москва', 'Московская область', 'Санкт-Петербург', 'Ленинградская область')
            and not isDead
            and sie.user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
            and user_segment not in ('Private.Seller', 'Private.AnimalShelter')
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    (case when region = 'Татарстан' then 'target' else region end) as region,
    sum(proxy_deals) as y 
from DMA.gmv_deals_proxy dp 
join items using (item_id)
where  event_date::date >= '20190101'
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

custom_sql:
with users_logcats as (
    select ci.user_id, 
        ci.item_id,
        ci.isDeliveryActive,
        cm.logical_category, 
        cm.logical_category_id, 
        ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
        row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
    from DMA.current_item ci 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
    where vertical in ('General', 'SpareParts')
        and (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
        and ci.StartTime >= '20160101'
),
user_segments as 
(
    select event_date, 
        ld.user_id, 
        ld.rnk, 
        ld.logical_category_id,
        ld.item_id,
        ld.isDeliveryActive,
        max(nvl(usm.segment_rank, ls.segment_rank)) over(partition by ld.user_id, ld.logical_category_id) as max_user_segment_rank
    from users_logcats ld
    left join dma.user_segment_market usm
           on usm.user_id = ld.user_id
          and usm.logical_category_id = ld.logical_category_id
          and usm.converting_date interpolate previous value ld.event_date
    -- в справочнике есть дефолтный сегмент для каждой логической категории
    left join dict.segmentation_ranks ls on ls.logical_category_id = ld.logical_category_id and ls.is_default
    where event_date >= '20170101'
        and ld.logical_category = 'General.HealthAndBeauty'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    'target' as region, 
    sum(new_listers_with_delivery)/sum(new_listers) as y
from 
    (
    select event_date,
        count(distinct hash(user_segments.user_id, logical_category_id)) as new_listers,
        count(distinct case when isDeliveryActive = True then item_id end) as new_listers_with_delivery
    from user_segments
    where rnk = 1 
        and max_user_segment_rank = 101
    group by 1 
    ) t
group by 1 
order by 1
limit 50000

from dma.click_stream_contacts cs 
inner join dma.current_item ci_vac on ci_vac.item_id = cs.item_id and cs.category_id = 250006 and ci_vac.Param1 ilike '%студенты%'
inner join dma.current_item ci on ci.user_id = cs.user_id and ci.category_id = 250004

                select Item_id, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION by Item_id order by Actual_date desc) as number_of_edition, Age from dds.S_Item_Age) as age_table 
                where number_of_edition = 1) age on ci.Item_id = age.Item_id and age between 14 and 24

and cs.eventdate::date >= '2019-04-01' 
group by 1 order by 1

custom_sql:
select  create_date::date as ds
    , case when 'Самарская область,Ставропольский край,Омская область,Оренбургская область,Тюменская область,Тверская область,Архангельская область,Забайкальский край,Бурятия,Курганская область,Камчатский край,Тыва' like '%'||cl.region ||'%' then 'target' 
        else cl.region        end as region
    , count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y        
from dma.current_order  co
join DMA.current_order_item
    using(deliveryorder_id)
join dma.current_microcategories cm

join dma.current_locations cl

custom_sql:
select
  pay_date::date as ds,
  (case
  when 'Свердловская область,Ставропольский край,Тюменская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target' else region
  end) as region,
  count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y 
 from dma.current_order co
  join DMA.current_order_item using(deliveryorder_id)
  join dma.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
  join dma.current_locations cl using(Location_id)
 where true
  AND create_date >= '20190101'
  and pay_date is not null
  and logical_category in ('General.Electronics') 
  and country = 'все регионы' -- 'Россия'
  and region NOT in ('Челябинская область','Омская область','Калининградская область','Тульская область','Курганская область',
  'Москва','Московская область','Санкт-Петербург','Ленинградская область','Башкортостан')
  and not is_test
  group by 1,2
  order by 1,2

select 
    cs.eventdate::date as ds, 
    case when Region in ('Москва','Санкт-Петербург','Уфа','Нижний Новгород','Екатеринбург','Новосибирск') then 'target' else Region end as region,
    count(distinct cs.user_id) as y
from dma.click_stream_contacts cs 
inner join dma.current_item ci_vac on ci_vac.item_id = cs.item_id and cs.category_id = 250006 and ci_vac.Param1 ilike '%студенты%'
inner join dma.current_locations cl on ci_vac.location_id = cl.location_id 
inner join dma.current_item ci on ci.user_id = cs.user_id and ci.category_id = 250004
inner join dma.item_day id on ci.item_id = id.item_id and id.event_date::date = cs.eventdate::date
inner join (select Item_id, Age from(
                select Item_id, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION by Item_id order by Actual_date desc) as number_of_edition, Age from dds.S_Item_Age) as age_table 
                where number_of_edition = 1) age on ci.Item_id = age.Item_id and age between 14 and 24
where cs.category_id = 250006 
and cs.eventdate::date >= '2019-04-01' 
group by 1,2  order by 1,2

custom_sql:
with items as
(
    select Item_id, region       
    from DMA.current_item sie 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = sie.microcat_id 
    join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = sie.location_id -- в gmv_deals_proxy не нашла Location_id поэтому оставила current_item
    join DMA.user_segment_market using(user_id)
    where  StartTime::date >= '20190101'
            and logical_category = 'General.ConstructionRenovation'
            and country = 'все регионы'
            and region not in ('Татарстан', 'Москва', 'Московская область', 'Санкт-Петербург', 'Ленинградская область')
            and not isDead
            and sie.user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
            and user_segment not in ('Private.Seller', 'Private.AnimalShelter')
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    (case when region = 'Нижегородская область' then 'target' else region end) as region,
    sum(proxy_deals) as y 
from DMA.gmv_deals_proxy dp 
join items using (item_id)
where  event_date::date >= '20190101'
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

custom_sql:
with region as 
(
    select participant_id as user_id, home_city_id as location_id,
    sum(1) cnt,
    row_number() over(partition by participant_id order by sum(1) desc) rn
    from dma.users_home_location_segment
    where participant_type = 'user'
    group by 1,2)
,region_by_home as 
(
    select user_id, location_id
    from region
    where rn = 1
)
,region_2 as 
(
    select user_id, location_id,
    sum(1) cnt,
    row_number() over(partition by user_id order by sum(1) desc) rn
    from dma.current_item
    group by 1,2
)
,region_by_item as 
(
    select user_id, location_id
    from region_2
    where rn = 1
)
,users as 
(
select distinct event_date,user_id from 
    (
    select event_date, user_id, lag(event_date) over(partition by user_id order by event_date) as last_event_date  from DMA.user_day
    where true 
        and page_views_total>0
    ) t
where true 
    and  (event_date::date - last_event_date::date >= 365*2 --не заходил 2 года
    or last_event_date is null) --ранее вообще не заходил
    and event_date>= getdate()::date - 365*4
),user_loc as 
(
select distinct
    u.event_date::date as ds,
    u.user_id,
    coalesce(rh.location_id,cu.location_id,ri.location_id) as location_id
from users u
join dma.current_user cu on u.user_id = cu.user_id
left join region_by_home rh on u.user_id = rh.user_id 
left join region_by_item ri on u.user_id = ri.user_id
)
select 
    ds,
    case when Region in  ('Новосибирская область') then 'target' else Region end as region, 
    count(User_id) as y
from user_loc ul
join DMA.current_locations cl using(Location_id)
group by 1,2

custom_sql:
with full_data as 
(
select * from public.ConstructionRenovation_user_cs_contacts_locations_20_22
union all 
select * from public.ConstructionRenovation_user_cs_contacts_locations_22_23
union all 
select EventDate::date as ds
    , csc.Cookie_id
    , csc.User_id
    , logical_category
    , param1
    , coalesce(loc.coord_city_id, loc.profile_location_id, loc.laas_location_id, loc.items_location_id) as user_location_id
from dma.click_stream_contacts csc 
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
left join dma.cookie_user_home_locations loc
                                            on csc.EventDate::date = loc.event_date
                                            and csc.cookie_id = loc.cookie_id
where EventDate::date > '20230301'
    and loc.event_date > '20230301'
    and logical_category = 'General.ConstructionRenovation'
)
select
    ds,
    (case when 'Краснодарский край,Свердловская область,Ростовская область,Башкортостан,Тюменская область,Челябинская область,Нижегородская область,Самарская область,Ставропольский край,Новосибирская область,Пермский край,Воронежская область,Омская область,Тверская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target'
    else region end) as region,
    count(distinct Cookie_id) as y 
from full_data csc
    join DMA.current_locations cl on csc.user_location_id = cl.location_id
where true
    and country = 'все регионы'
    and region not in ('Санкт-Петербург','Краснодарский край','Ленинградская область','Красноярский край')
    and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
group by 1,2

SELECT 
    metric_date as ds ,
  'target' as region ,
  sum(metric_value) as y
FROM   dma.big10_abs
WHERE  true
   and is_asd = -1
   and platform in ('android', 'ios')
   and user_segment_market = 'any'
   and metric_date >= date_trunc('year', timestampadd(year,-4, current_timestamp))::date
   and metric_name = 'buyers'
   and vertical_id in (SELECT DISTINCT vertical_id
                    FROM   dma.current_microcategories
                    WHERE  vertical = 'Services')
   and logical_category_id in (SELECT DISTINCT logical_category_id
                            FROM   dma.current_microcategories
                            WHERE  logical_category in ('Services.Appliances','Services.Business','Services.HealthAndBeauty','Services.MajorRepair','Services.MinorRepair','Services.TransportationAndDelivery'))
   and target_type = 'fact'

custom_sql:
with items as
(
    select Item_id, city, region       
    from DMA.current_item sie 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = sie.microcat_id 
    join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = sie.location_id -- в gmv_deals_proxy не нашла Location_id поэтому оставила current_item
    where  StartTime::date >= '20190101'
            and vertical = 'SpareParts'
            -- and vertical = 'General'
            and country = 'все регионы'
            and (city = 'Владивосток' 
                or region not in ('Бурятия', 'Саха (Якутия)', 'Забайкальский край', 'Камчатский край', 'Приморский край', 'Хабаровский край', 
                                'Амурская область', 'Магаданская область', 'Сахалинская область', 'Еврейская АО', 'Чукотский АО'))
            and not isDead
            and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    (case when city = 'Владивосток' then 'target' else region end) as region,
    sum(proxy_deals) as y 
from DMA.gmv_deals_proxy dp 
join items using (item_id)
where  event_date::date >= '20190101'
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

with items as
(
    select Item_id, city, (case when 'Краснодар,Тюмень,Тверь' like '%'||cl.city||'%' then 'target'
    else city end) as region           
    from DMA.current_item sie 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = sie.microcat_id 
    join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = sie.location_id
    where  StartTime::date >= '20190101'
            and vertical = 'SpareParts'
            and country = 'все регионы'
            and city in ('Краснодар','Тюмень','Тверь','Ростов-на-Дону','Челябинск','Ставрополь')
            and not isDead
            and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    region,
    sum(proxy_deals) as y 
from DMA.gmv_deals_proxy dp 
join items using (item_id)
where  event_date::date >= '20190101'
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

custom_sql:
select pay_date::date as ds
, (case when 'Нижний Новгород,Воронеж,Екатеринбург,Ростов-на-Дону,Самара,Волгоград,Казань,Томск,Тула,Ижевск,Ставрополь,Барнаул,Тверь,Новосибирск,Красноярск' like '%'||cl.city||'%' then 'target'
else city end) as region
, count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y
from dma.current_order co
join DMA.current_order_item
using(deliveryorder_id)
join dma.current_microcategories cm
using(microcat_id)
join dma.current_locations cl
using(Location_id)
where create_date >= '20190101'
and pay_date is not null
and (vertical = 'General'  or vertical = 'SpareParts') 
and country = 'все регионы'
and city in ('Нижний Новгород','Воронеж','Екатеринбург','Ростов-на-Дону','Самара','Волгоград','Казань','Томск','Тула','Ижевск','Ставрополь','Барнаул','Тверь','Новосибирск','Красноярск','Киров','Оренбург','Тюмень','Иваново','Владимир','Пенза','Чебоксары','Ханты-Мансийск',
'Петрозаводск','Великий Новгород','Йошкар-Ола','Мурманск','Тамбов','Махачкала','Сыктывкар')
and not is_test
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

SELECT 
    metric_date as ds ,
  'target' as region ,
  sum(metric_value) as y
FROM   dma.big10_abs
WHERE  true
   and is_asd = -1
   and platform in ('avito.ru', 'm.avito.ru')
   and user_segment_market = 'any'
   and metric_date >= date_trunc('year', timestampadd(year,-4, current_timestamp))::date
   and metric_name = 'buyers'
   and vertical_id in (SELECT DISTINCT vertical_id
                    FROM   dma.current_microcategories
                    WHERE  vertical = 'Services')
   and logical_category_id in (SELECT DISTINCT logical_category_id
                            FROM   dma.current_microcategories
                            WHERE  logical_category in ('Services.Appliances','Services.Business','Services.HealthAndBeauty','Services.MajorRepair','Services.MinorRepair','Services.TransportationAndDelivery'))
   and target_type = 'fact'
GROUP BY 1,2

select 
    EventDate::date as ds, 
    case when Region in ('Москва','Санкт-Петербург','Уфа','Нижний Новгород','Екатеринбург','Новосибирск') then 'target' else Region end as region,
    count(distinct Cookie_id) as y 
from dma.click_stream_contacts id
inner join dma.current_item ci using(Item_id)
inner join dma.current_locations cl on id.location_id = cl.location_id 
where ci.category_id = 250006 
and EventDate::date >= '2019-04-01' and Param1 ilike '%студенты%'
group by 1,2 order by 1

custom_sql:
with users_logcats as (
    select ci.user_id, 
        ci.item_id,
        ci.isDeliveryActive,
        cm.logical_category, 
        cm.logical_category_id, 
        ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
        row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
    from DMA.current_item ci 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
    where vertical in ('General', 'SpareParts')
        and (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
        and ci.StartTime >= '20160101'
),
user_segments as 
(
    select event_date, 
        ld.user_id, 
        ld.rnk, 
        ld.logical_category_id,
        ld.item_id,
        ld.isDeliveryActive,
        max(nvl(usm.segment_rank, ls.segment_rank)) over(partition by ld.user_id, ld.logical_category_id) as max_user_segment_rank
    from users_logcats ld
    left join dma.user_segment_market usm
           on usm.user_id = ld.user_id
          and usm.logical_category_id = ld.logical_category_id
          and usm.converting_date interpolate previous value ld.event_date
    -- в справочнике есть дефолтный сегмент для каждой логической категории
    left join dict.segmentation_ranks ls on ls.logical_category_id = ld.logical_category_id and ls.is_default
    where event_date >= '20170101'
        and ld.logical_category = 'General.Electronics'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    'target' as region, 
    sum(new_listers_with_delivery)/sum(new_listers) as y
from 
    (
    select event_date,
        count(distinct hash(user_segments.user_id, logical_category_id)) as new_listers,
        count(distinct case when isDeliveryActive = True then item_id end) as new_listers_with_delivery
    from user_segments
    where rnk = 1 
        and max_user_segment_rank = 101
    group by 1 
    ) t

select  first_contact_event_date::date as ds
        , (case when region in ('Омская область')  then 'target' else region end) as region
        , count(distinct csc.cookie_id) as y        
from DMA.buyer_birthday csc 
join DMA.users_home_location_segment uhl on csc.cookie_id = uhl.participant_id and participant_type = 'visitor'
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = uhl.home_city_id
where first_contact_event_date::date >= '2019-01-01'
        and region != 'Undefined'
        and Population>=100000
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

select
    activation_time::date as ds,
    'target' as region,
    count(distinct ia.item_id) as y
from dma.item_activations ia
join dma.current_item using(Item_id)
join dma.jobs_vacancies_duplicates_daily jvdd on jvdd.item_id = ia.item_id and jvdd.event_date = ia.activation_time::date 
where activation_time::date >= '2020-01-01'
    and activation_avitoversion_id <> 6
    and is_item_start
    and is_original
    and activation_type <> 'Wait'
    and Category_id = 250006
group by 1
order by 1

with users_logcats as (
    select ci.user_id, 
        ci.item_id,
        cm.logical_category_id, 
        ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
        ci.location_id,
        row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
    from DMA.current_item ci 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
    where (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
        and ci.StartTime >= '20190101'
        and vertical = 'Realty'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    'target' as region, 
    count(distinct user_id) as y
from users_logcats ld
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = ld.location_id
where rnk = 1 
    and event_date >= '20190101'
    and country = 'все регионы'
group by 1

custom_sql:
select  EventDate::date as ds
        , (case when city = 'Владивосток' then 'target' else region end) as region
        , count(distinct Cookie_id) as y        
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc 
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
join DMA.current_locations cl using(location_id)
where EventDate::date >= '20190101' 
        and vertical = 'SpareParts'
        -- and vertical = 'General'
        and country = 'все регионы'
        and (city = 'Владивосток' 
            or region not in ('Бурятия', 'Саха (Якутия)', 'Забайкальский край', 'Камчатский край', 'Приморский край', 'Хабаровский край', 
                            'Амурская область', 'Магаданская область', 'Сахалинская область', 'Еврейская АО', 'Чукотский АО'))
        and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
        and item_id not in (select item_id from dma.current_item where isDead)
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

select  create_date::date as ds
    , case when 'Санкт-Петербург,Ленинградская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target' 
        else cl.region        end as region
    , count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y        
from dma.current_order  co
join DMA.current_order_item
    using(deliveryorder_id)
join dma.current_microcategories cm
    using(microcat_id)
join dma.current_locations cl 
    on  co.buyer_location_id = cl.location_id
where     true
    and ('Карелия,Калининградская область,Новгородская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' or 'Санкт-Петербург,Ленинградская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%')
    and create_date > current_date - 366*4
    and pay_date is not null
    and vertical = 'General'
    and logical_category = 'General.GoodsForChildren'
group by 1,2

custom_sql:
with users_logcats as (
    select ci.user_id, 
        ci.item_id,
        ci.isDeliveryActive,
        cm.logical_category, 
        cm.logical_category_id, 
        ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
        row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
    from DMA.current_item ci 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
    where vertical in ('General', 'SpareParts')
        and (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
        and ci.StartTime >= '20160101'
),
user_segments as 
(
    select event_date, 
        ld.user_id, 
        ld.rnk, 
        ld.logical_category_id,
        ld.item_id,
        ld.isDeliveryActive,
        max(nvl(usm.segment_rank, ls.segment_rank)) over(partition by ld.user_id, ld.logical_category_id) as max_user_segment_rank
    from users_logcats ld
    left join dma.user_segment_market usm
           on usm.user_id = ld.user_id
          and usm.logical_category_id = ld.logical_category_id
          and usm.converting_date interpolate previous value ld.event_date
    -- в справочнике есть дефолтный сегмент для каждой логической категории
    left join dict.segmentation_ranks ls on ls.logical_category_id = ld.logical_category_id and ls.is_default
    where event_date >= '20170101'
        and ld.logical_category = 'General.Fashion'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    'target' as region, 
    sum(new_listers_with_delivery)/sum(new_listers) as y
from 
    (
    select event_date,
        count(distinct hash(user_segments.user_id, logical_category_id)) as new_listers,
        count(distinct case when isDeliveryActive = True then item_id end) as new_listers_with_delivery
    from user_segments
    where rnk = 1 
        and max_user_segment_rank = 101
    group by 1 
    ) t
group by 1 
order by 1
limit 50000

custom_sql:
with items as 
(
select 
    id.item_id
    ,date_trunc('month',event_date)::date as month
    ,region
   -- ,max(ci.user_id) as User_id
    ,max(cm.microcat_id) as microcat_id
   -- ,max(logical_category_id) as logical_category_id
    --,max(ci.infmquery_id) as infmquery_id
from DMA.item_day id 
join DMA.current_item ci using(Item_id)
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
join dma.current_locations using (Location_id)
where true 
    and ci.user_id not in (select user_id from DMA.current_user where IsTest)
    and cm.vertical in ('General')
    and cm.subcategory_name in ('Мебель и интерьер','Посуда и товары для кухни')
    and cm.microcat_id >0 and cm.is_active_microcat and cm.microcat_name not ilike '%услуги%'
    --and event_date >= '2021-01-01'
    and event_date >= getdate()::Date -7 
    --and event_date in ('2022-10-27','2022-03-05')
group by 1,2,3
),
titles as 
    (
    select 
        item_id
        ,title
        ,row_number() over(partition by Item_id order by actual_date desc) as rn 
    from DDS.S_Item_Title
    where true
        and Item_id in (select distinct item_id from items)
    ),
title_unique as 
    (
    select 
        item_id
        ,title
    from titles
    where rn = 1
    ),
items_titles as
(
select 
    t.item_id
    ,lower(
            replace(
                regexp_replace(
                    title
                    , '[^0-9a-zA-Zа-яА-ЯёЁ]+', ' '
                )
                , E'\1', ''
            )::varchar(128) 
        ) as title
    ,case when (title not ilike ('%как икеа%') and title not ilike ('%как икея%') and title not ilike ('%как ikea%') 
            and title not ilike ('%как в ikea%') and title not ilike ('%как в икеа%') and title not ilike ('%как в икея%')) then 0 
            else 1 end as is_replica
    ,count(*)
from items
join title_unique t using(item_id)
WHERE true
    and isutf8(title)
    and (title ilike ('%икеа%') or title ilike ('%икея%')  or title ilike ('%ikea%') ) 
   -- and (title not ilike ('%как икеа%') or title not ilike ('%как ikea%') or title not ilike ('%как в ikea%') or title not ilike ('%как в икеа%'))
group by 1,2,3
)
select
    EventDate::date as ds,
    (case when 'Москва, Санкт-Петербург, Московская область, Краснодарский край, Свердловская область, Татарстан, Новосибирская область, Ленинградская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target' else region end) as region,
    count(distinct Cookie_id) as y 
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
    join DMA.current_locations cl using(location_id)
where true
    and EventDate::date >= '20190101' 
    and cm.subcategory_name in ('Мебель и интерьер','Посуда и товары для кухни')
    and csc.item_id in (select distinct item_id from items_titles)
    and country =  'все регионы'
    and region not in ('Краснодарский край','Самарская область','Воронежская область')
    and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

custom_sql:
SELECT event_date as ds ,
       case when locationname in ('Ростовская область','Татарстан','Челябинская область',
                                  'Нижегородская область','Ставропольский край','Новосибирская область',
                                  'Воронежская область','Волгоградская область','Иркутская область',
                                  'Алтайский край','Омская область','Ярославская область',
                                  'Оренбургская область','Тульская область','Владимирская область') then 'target'
            else locationname end as region ,
       sum(metric_value) as y
FROM   dma.regional_ab_metrics ab join dma.current_locations cl using (location_id)
WHERE  user_segment_market = 'any'
   and is_user_asd = 'any'
   and cl.isactive
   and cl.city_population_group != 'under_100k'
   and platform_id = 4
   and event_date >= date_trunc('year', timestampadd(year,-4, current_timestamp))::date
   and logical_category_id in (select distinct logical_category_id from dma.current_microcategories where logical_category = 'General.Electronics')
   and metric_name = 'buyers'
   and ab.location_id not in (SELECT location_id
                           FROM   dma.current_locations
                           WHERE  isactive

custom_sql:
with region as 
(
    select participant_id as user_id, home_city_id as location_id,
    sum(1) cnt,
    row_number() over(partition by participant_id order by sum(1) desc) rn
    from dma.users_home_location_segment
    where participant_type = 'user'
    group by 1,2)
,region_by_home as 
(
    select user_id, location_id
    from region
    where rn = 1
)
,region_2 as 
(
    select user_id, location_id,
    sum(1) cnt,
    row_number() over(partition by user_id order by sum(1) desc) rn
    from dma.current_item
    group by 1,2
)
,region_by_item as 
(
    select user_id, location_id
    from region_2
    where rn = 1
)
,users as 
(
select distinct event_date,user_id from 
    (
    select event_date, user_id, lag(event_date) over(partition by user_id order by event_date) as last_event_date  from DMA.user_day
    where true 
        and page_views_total>0
    ) t
where true 
    and (event_date::date - last_event_date::date  >= 365 --не заходил год
    or last_event_date is null) --ранее вообще не заходил
    and event_date>= getdate()::date - 365*4
),user_loc as 
(
select distinct
    u.event_date::date as ds,
    u.user_id,
    coalesce(rh.location_id,cu.location_id,ri.location_id) as location_id
from users u
join dma.current_user cu on u.user_id = cu.user_id
left join region_by_home rh on u.user_id = rh.user_id 
left join region_by_item ri on u.user_id = ri.user_id
)
select 
    ds,
    case when Region in  ('Волгоградская область','Саратовская область') then 'target' else Region end as region, 
    count(User_id) as y
from user_loc ul
join DMA.current_locations cl using(Location_id)
group by 1,2

custom_sql:
select  EventDate::date as ds
        , (case when city = 'Владивосток' then 'target' else region end) as region
        , count(distinct Cookie_id) as y        
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc 
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
join DMA.current_locations cl using(location_id)
where EventDate::date >= '20190101' 
        -- and vertical = 'SpareParts'
        and vertical = 'General'
        and country = 'все регионы'
        and (city = 'Владивосток' 
            or region not in ('Бурятия', 'Саха (Якутия)', 'Забайкальский край', 'Камчатский край', 'Приморский край', 'Хабаровский край', 
                            'Амурская область', 'Магаданская область', 'Сахалинская область', 'Еврейская АО', 'Чукотский АО'))
        and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
        and item_id not in (select item_id from dma.current_item where isDead)

SELECT event_date as ds ,
       case when locationname in ('Краснодарский край','Свердловская область','Башкортостан','Самарская область','Дагестан','Кемеровская область','Саратовская область','Тюменская область','Ханты-Мансийский АО','Удмуртия','Белгородская область','Калининградская область','Вологодская область','Рязанская область','Ульяновская область') then 'target'
            else locationname end as region ,
       sum(metric_value) as y
FROM   dma.regional_ab_metrics ab join dma.current_locations cl using (location_id)

select
    event_date as ds, 
    case when Region in ('Орловская область','Рязанская область','Брянская область','Владимирская область') then 'target' else region end as region, 
    count(uc.user_id) as y from DMA.user_cohort uc
where event_date::Date >= getdate()::date - 365*4
group by 1,2

select  create_date::date as ds
    , case when 'Свердловская область,Челябинская область,Тюменская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target' 
        else cl.region        end as region
    , count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y        
from dma.current_order  co
join DMA.current_order_item
    using(deliveryorder_id)
join dma.current_microcategories cm
    using(microcat_id)
join dma.current_locations cl 
    on  co.buyer_location_id = cl.location_id
where     true
    and ('Омская область,Томская область,Курганская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' or 'Свердловская область,Челябинская область,Тюменская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%')
    and create_date > current_date - 366*4
    and pay_date is not null
    and vertical = 'General'
group by 1,2

custom_sql:
with items as
(
    select Item_id, region       
    from DMA.current_item sie 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = sie.microcat_id 
    join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = sie.location_id -- в gmv_deals_proxy не нашла Location_id поэтому оставила current_item
    where  StartTime::date >= '20190101'
            and logical_category = 'General.ConstructionRenovation'
            and country = 'все регионы'
            and region not in ('Нижегородска область', 'Москва', 'Московская область', 'Санкт-Петербург', 'Ленинградская область')
            and not isDead
            and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    (case when region = 'Татарстан' then 'target' else region end) as region,
    sum(proxy_deals) as y 
from DMA.gmv_deals_proxy dp 
join items using (item_id)
where  event_date::date >= '20190101'
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

select pay_date::date as ds
    , (case when 'Екатеринбург' like '%'||cl.city||'%' then 'target'
    else city end) as region
    , count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y
from dma.current_order co
join DMA.current_order_item
    using(deliveryorder_id)
join dma.current_microcategories cm
    using(microcat_id)
join dma.current_locations cl
    on cl.Location_id = co.buyer_location_id
where create_date >= '20200101'
    and pay_date is not null
    and vertical = 'General'
    and logical_category = 'General.Electronics'
    and country = 'все регионы'
    and city in ('Екатеринбург','Самара','Уфа','Омск')
    and not is_test
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

select activation_time::date as ds
    , case when 'Владимирская область,Калужская область, Нижегородская область, Ростовская область,  Самарская область,Свердловская область, Тверская область,Тульская область,Ярославская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target' 
        else cl.region end as region
    , count(distinct case when isDeliveryActive is true then ia.item_id end)/count(distinct ia.item_id)*100 as y
from DMA.item_activations ia 
join dma.current_item using(Item_id)
join dma.current_locations cl using(Location_id)
join dma.current_microcategories using(microcat_id)

and (subcategory_id = 37 or subcategory_id = 52) 
group by 1,2

    , case when 'Владимирская область,Калужская область, Нижегородская область, Ростовская область,  Самарская область,Свердловская область, Тверская область,Тульская область,Ярославская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target'

custom_sql:
select pay_date::date as ds
    , (case when 'Нижний Новгород' like '%'||cl.city||'%' then 'target'
    else city end) as region
    , count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y
from dma.current_order co
join DMA.current_order_item
    using(deliveryorder_id)
join dma.current_microcategories cm
    using(microcat_id)
join dma.current_locations cl
    on cl.Location_id = co.buyer_location_id
where create_date >= '20200101'
    and pay_date is not null
    and vertical = 'General'
    and logical_category = 'General.Electronics'
    and country = 'все регионы'
    and city in ('Нижний Новгород','Самара','Пермь','Воронеж')
    and not is_test
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

with users_logcats as (
select ci.user_id,
ci.item_id,
cm.logical_category_id,
ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
ci.location_id,
row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
from DMA.current_item ci
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
where true
and (vertical = 'General'  or vertical = 'SpareParts') 
and (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
and ci.StartTime >= '20190101'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
(case when 'Нижний Новгород,Воронеж,Екатеринбург,Ростов-на-Дону,Самара,Волгоград,Казань,Томск,Тула,Ижевск,Ставрополь,Барнаул,Тверь,Новосибирск,Красноярск' like '%'||cl.city||'%' then 'target'
else city end) as region,
count(distinct user_id) as y
from users_logcats ld
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = ld.location_id
where event_date >= '20190101'
and rnk = 1
and country = 'все регионы'
and city in ('Нижний Новгород','Воронеж','Екатеринбург','Ростов-на-Дону','Самара','Волгоград','Казань','Томск','Тула','Ижевск','Ставрополь','Барнаул','Тверь','Новосибирск','Красноярск','Киров','Оренбург','Тюмень','Иваново','Владимир','Пенза','Чебоксары','Ханты-Мансийск',
'Петрозаводск','Великий Новгород','Йошкар-Ола','Мурманск','Тамбов','Махачкала','Сыктывкар')
group by 1,2

custom_sql:
with items as
(
    select Item_id, city, region       
    from DMA.current_item sie 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = sie.microcat_id 
    join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = sie.location_id -- в gmv_deals_proxy не нашла Location_id поэтому оставила current_item
    where  StartTime::date >= '20190101'
            and vertical = 'SpareParts'
            -- and vertical = 'General'
            and country = 'все регионы'
            and (city = 'Владивосток' 
                or region not in ('Бурятия', 'Саха (Якутия)', 'Забайкальский край', 'Камчатский край', 'Приморский край', 'Хабаровский край', 
                                'Амурская область', 'Магаданская область', 'Сахалинская область', 'Еврейская АО', 'Чукотский АО'))
            and not isDead
            and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    (case when city = 'Владивосток' then 'target' else region end) as region,
    sum(proxy_deals) as y 
from DMA.gmv_deals_proxy dp 
join items using (item_id)
where  event_date::date >= '20190101'
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

custom_sql:
select  pay_date::date as ds
        , (case when 'Краснодарский край,Свердловская область,Ростовская область,Башкортостан,Тюменская область,Челябинская область,Нижегородская область,Самарская область,Ставропольский край,Новосибирская область,Пермский край,Воронежская область,Омская область,Тверская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target'
           else region end) as region
        , count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y       
    from dma.current_order  co
    join DMA.current_order_item
        using(deliveryorder_id)
    join dma.current_microcategories cm
        using(microcat_id)
    join dma.current_locations cl
        using(Location_id)
    where create_date >= '20200330'
        and pay_date is not null
        and vertical = 'General'
        and logical_category = 'General.ConstructionRenovation'
        and country = 'все регионы'
        and region not in ('Санкт-Петербург','Краснодарский край','Ленинградская область','Красноярский край')
    group by 1,2
    order by 1,2

custom_sql:
select EventDate::date as ds
, (case when 'Иркутская область,Кемеровская область,Ямало-Ненецкий АО' like '%'||cl.region||'%' 
    or 'Екатеринбург,Нижнекамск' like '%'||cl.City||'%' then 'target'
    when 'Тюменская область,Красноярский край,Новосибирская область,Воронежская область,Костромская область,Амурская область,Брянская область,Ростовская область,Томская область,Еврейская АО,Крым' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then region 
    else city end) as region
, count(distinct csc.Cookie_id) as y
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
join DMA.current_locations cl using(location_id)
join DMA.buyer_birthday bb on bb.Cookie_id = csc.Cookie_id and bb.first_contact_event_date = csc.EventDate
where EventDate::date >= '20190101'
and (vertical = 'General'  or vertical = 'SpareParts')
and logical_category = 'General.Electronics'
and country = 'все регионы'
and (('Иркутская область,Кемеровская область,Ростовская область,Ямало-Ненецкий АО,Томская область,Еврейская АО,Новосибирская область,Воронежская область,Костромская область,Амурская область,Брянская область,Красноярский край,Тюменская область,Крым') like '%'||cl.region||'%'
    or ('Киров,,Уфа,Улан-Удэ,Комсомольск-на-Амуре,Нижнекамск,Екатеринбург') like '%'||cl.City||'%' )
and item_id not in (select item_id from dma.current_item where isDead)
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

WITH region_date_range AS
(
    SELECT  event_date as _date
           ,t.region
    FROM dict.calendar
    CROSS JOIN
    (
        SELECT  distinct region
        FROM dma.current_locations
        WHERE Country = 'все регионы'
        AND region not IN ('Undefined', 'другой регион')
        AND IsActive
        AND Logical_Level_Name != 'Meta regions' 
    ) t
    WHERE true
    AND event_date BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND CURRENT_DATE()-1
    ORDER BY 1 desc, 2 
), raw_item_started AS
(
    SELECT _date, region, sum(1) as item_started FROM (
        SELECT  s.user_id    AS _subject
               ,s.event_date AS _date
               ,cl.region    AS region
        FROM dma.o_seller_item_event s
        JOIN dma.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
        JOIN dma.current_locations cl using(location_id)
        LEFT JOIN dma.user_segment_market usm
        ON s.user_id = usm.user_id AND usm.logical_category_id = 24144500001 AND s.event_date interpolate previous value usm.converting_date
        WHERE true
        AND s.event_date >= '2019-01-01'
        AND cm.logical_category_id = 24144500001 -- Transport.UsedCars
        AND activation_type != 'Wait'
        AND is_item_start = True
        AND COALESCE(usm.user_segment, 'Private.Seller') not IN ('Enterprise.DealerHolding', 'MidMarket.Dealer') -- хардкод, для UsedCars сегмент по умолчанию Private.Seller
        AND cl.country = 'все регионы'
        AND cl.region not IN ('Undefined', 'другой регион')
        AND cl.IsActive
        AND cl.Logical_Level_Name != 'Meta regions' 
        ) t GROUP BY _date, region
), exclude_regs as 
(
    SELECT distinct rdr.region 
    FROM region_date_range rdr 
    LEFT JOIN raw_item_started ris ON rdr._date = ris._date and rdr.region = ris.region
    WHERE ris.item_started is null
)
SELECT  _date                                                                                                                         AS ds
       ,(case WHEN region IN ('Москва','Московская область','Санкт-Петербург','Ленинградская область') THEN 'target' else region end) AS region
       ,item_started                                                                                                                  AS y
FROM raw_item_started 
WHERE true
    AND region not in (SELECT region FROM exclude_regs)

with items as
(
    select Item_id, city, region       
    from DMA.current_item sie 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm on cm.microcat_id = sie.microcat_id 
    join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = sie.location_id -- в gmv_deals_proxy не нашла Location_id поэтому оставила current_item
    where  StartTime::date >= '20190101'
            -- and vertical = 'SpareParts'
            and vertical = 'General'
            and country = 'все регионы'
            and (city = 'Владивосток' 
                or region not in ('Бурятия', 'Саха (Якутия)', 'Забайкальский край', 'Камчатский край', 'Приморский край', 'Хабаровский край',

            and not isDead
            and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    (case when city = 'Владивосток' then 'target' else region end) as region,
    sum(proxy_deals) as y 
from DMA.gmv_deals_proxy dp 
join items using (item_id)
where  event_date::date >= '20190101'
group by 1,2

custom_sql:
select activation_time::date as ds
    , case when 'Владимирская область,Калужская область, Нижегородская область, Ростовская область,  Самарская область,Свердловская область, Тверская область,Тульская область,Ярославская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target' 
        else cl.region end as region
    , count(distinct case when isDeliveryActive is true then ia.item_id end)/count(distinct ia.item_id)*100 as y
from DMA.item_activations ia 
join dma.current_item using(Item_id)
join dma.current_locations cl using(Location_id)
join dma.current_microcategories using(microcat_id) 
where is_item_start = false
and is_after_ttl = true
and activation_time::date >= '2018-07-20' 
and (subcategory_id = 37 or subcategory_id = 52) 
group by 1,2

select  create_date::date as ds
    , case when 'Москва,Московская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target' 
        else cl.region        end as region
    , count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y        
from dma.current_order  co
join DMA.current_order_item
    using(deliveryorder_id)
join dma.current_microcategories cm
    using(microcat_id)
join dma.current_locations cl 
    on  co.buyer_location_id = cl.location_id
where     true
    and ('Владимирская область,Адыгея,Калужская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' or 'Москва,Московская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%')
    and create_date > current_date - 366*4
    and pay_date is not null
    and vertical = 'General'
    and logical_category in ('General.Electronics','General.Fashion','General.GoodsForChildren')
group by 1,2

with full_data as 
(
select * from public.gfpopova_user_cs_contacts_locations_20_22
where logical_category = 'General.Electronics'
union all 
select * from public.gfpopova_user_cs_contacts_locations_22_23
where logical_category = 'General.Electronics'
union all 
select EventDate::date as ds
    , csc.Cookie_id
    , csc.User_id
    , logical_category
    , coalesce(loc.coord_city_id, loc.profile_location_id, loc.laas_location_id, loc.items_location_id) as user_location_id
from dma.click_stream_contacts csc 
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
left join dma.cookie_user_home_locations loc
                                            on csc.EventDate::date = loc.event_date
                                            and csc.cookie_id = loc.cookie_id
where EventDate::date > '20230301'
    and loc.event_date > '20230301'
    and vertical = 'General'
    and logical_category = 'General.Electronics'
    and user_location_id in (22,346,992,1294,1344,3771,3976,4145)
)
-- select year(ds), region, count(distinct ds) from (
select
    ds,
    (case when 'Нижний Новгород' like '%'||cl.city||'%' then 'target'
    else city end) as region,
    count(distinct hash(Cookie_id,logical_category)) as y 
from full_data csc
    join DMA.current_locations cl on csc.user_location_id = cl.location_id
where true
    and country =  'все регионы'
    and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
    and city in ('Нижний Новгород','Самара','Пермь','Воронеж')
group by 1,2 
-- ) _ group by 1,2 
order by 1,2

with users_logcats as (
    select ci.user_id, 
        ci.item_id,
        cm.logical_category_id, 
        ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
        ci.location_id,
        row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
    from DMA.current_item ci 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
    where (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
        and ci.StartTime >= '20190101'
        and vertical = 'General'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    'target' as region, 
    count(distinct user_id) as y
from users_logcats ld
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = ld.location_id
where rnk = 1 
    and event_date >= '20190101'
    and country = 'все регионы'
group by 1

with full_data as

select * from public.spareparts_user_cs_contacts_locations_20_22
union all 
select * from public.spareparts_user_cs_contacts_locations_22_23
union all 
select EventDate::date as ds
    , csc.Cookie_id
    , csc.User_id
    , logical_category
    , csc.microcat_id
    , coalesce(loc.coord_city_id, loc.profile_location_id, loc.laas_location_id, loc.items_location_id) as user_location_id
from dma.click_stream_contacts csc 
join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
left join dma.cookie_user_home_locations loc
                                            on csc.EventDate::date = loc.event_date
                                            and csc.cookie_id = loc.cookie_id
where EventDate::date > '20230301'
    and loc.event_date > '20230301'
    and logical_category = 'SpareParts.SpareParts'
    and user_location_id in (343,547,1261,1788,2840,3193)
)

custom_sql:
with users_logcats as (
    select ci.user_id, 
        ci.item_id,
        cm.logical_category_id, 
        ci.StartTime::date as event_date,
        ci.location_id,
        row_number() over (partition by ci.user_id, cm.logical_category_id order by ci.StartTime asc) as rnk
    from DMA.current_item ci 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(Microcat_id)
    where (not ci.isdead or datediff('day', ci.StartTime, ci.death_date) >= 30)
        and ci.StartTime >= '20190101'
)
select event_date::date as ds,
    'target' as region, 
    count(distinct user_id) as y
from users_logcats ld
join DMA.current_locations cl on cl.location_id = ld.location_id
where rnk = 1 
    and event_date >= '20190101'
    and country = 'все регионы'
group by 1

select 
    EventDate::date as ds,
    (case when 'Новосибирская область,Удмуртия,Оренбургская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%'
        then 'target' 
        else region end) as region,
    count(distinct Cookie_id) as y 
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
    join DMA.current_locations cl using(location_id)
where EventDate::date >=  '20200101' 
    and logical_category = 'General.Furniture'
    and region in 
        (
        'Новосибирская область','Удмуртия','Оренбургская область','Татарстан','Кемеровская область','Томская область'
        )
    and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
    and item_id not in (select item_id from dma.current_item where isDead)
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

select 
    EventDate::date as ds,
    (case when 'Краснодарский край,Иркутская область,Владимирская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%'
        then 'target' 
        else region end) as region,
    count(distinct Cookie_id) as y 
from DMA.click_stream_contacts csc 
    join DMA.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
    join DMA.current_locations cl using(location_id)
where EventDate::date >=  '20200101' 
    and logical_category = 'General.Furniture'
    and region in 
        (
        'Краснодарский край','Иркутская область','Владимирская область','Ростовская область','Ставропольский край','Крым'
        )
    and user_id not in (select user_id from dma.current_user where isTest)
    and item_id not in (select item_id from dma.current_item where isDead)
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

WITH region_date_range AS
(
    SELECT  event_date as _date
           ,t.region
    FROM dict.calendar
    CROSS JOIN
    (
        SELECT  distinct region
        FROM dma.current_locations
        WHERE Country = 'все регионы'
        AND region not IN ('Undefined', 'другой регион')
        AND IsActive
        AND Logical_Level_Name != 'Meta regions' 
    ) t
    WHERE true
    AND event_date BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND CURRENT_DATE()-1
    ORDER BY 1 desc, 2 
), raw_item_started AS
(
    SELECT _date, region, sum(1) as item_started FROM (
        SELECT  s.user_id    AS _subject
               ,s.event_date AS _date
               ,cl.region    AS region
        FROM dma.o_seller_item_event s
        JOIN dma.current_microcategories cm using(microcat_id)
        JOIN dma.current_locations cl using(location_id)
        LEFT JOIN dma.user_segment_market usm
        ON s.user_id = usm.user_id AND usm.logical_category_id = 24144500001 AND s.event_date interpolate previous value usm.converting_date
        WHERE true
        AND s.event_date >= '2019-01-01'
        AND cm.logical_category_id = 24144500001 -- Transport.UsedCars
        AND activation_type != 'Wait'
        AND is_item_start = True
        AND COALESCE(usm.user_segment, 'Private.Seller') not IN ('Enterprise.DealerHolding', 'MidMarket.Dealer') -- хардкод, для UsedCars сегмент по умолчанию Private.Seller
        AND cl.country = 'все регионы'
        AND cl.region not IN ('Undefined', 'другой регион')
        AND cl.IsActive
        AND cl.Logical_Level_Name != 'Meta regions' 
        ) t GROUP BY _date, region
), exclude_regs as 
(
    SELECT distinct rdr.region 
    FROM region_date_range rdr 
    LEFT JOIN raw_item_started ris ON rdr._date = ris._date and rdr.region = ris.region
    WHERE ris.item_started is null
)
SELECT  _date                                                                                                                         AS ds
       ,(case WHEN region IN ('Москва','Московская область','Санкт-Петербург','Ленинградская область') THEN 'target' else region end) AS region
       ,item_started                                                                                                                  AS y
FROM raw_item_started 
WHERE true
    AND region not in (SELECT region FROM exclude_regs)

covariates_sql:
with prices as 
(
select  re.event_date,
        re.Item_id,
        price/area as price_per_metr,
        SFAccount_Type
from DMA.re_item_day as re  join DMA.current_microcategories as cm using(Microcat_id)
                            join DMA.current_item as ci using(Item_id)
                            left join dma.salesforce_usermapping as su using(User_id)
where 1 
and region='Москва' 
and logical_category in ('Realty.NewDevelopments')
and event_date>='2019-01-01'
)
, prices_median as 
(
select   
        event_date,
        approximate_median(price_per_metr) AS price_median
from prices
group by event_date
)
, prices_median_dev as 
(
select  
        event_date,
        approximate_median(price_per_metr) AS price_median_developer
from prices
where 1 
and SFAccount_Type = 'Девелопер'
group by event_date
)
, item_qty as 
(
select  re.event_date,
        sum(case when logical_category='Realty.NewDevelopments' then 1 else 0 end) as nd_item_qty,
        sum(case when logical_category='Realty.NewDevelopments' and SFAccount_Type='Девелопер' then 1 else 0 end) as nd_item_qty_developer,
        sum(case when logical_category='Realty.SecondarySell' then 1 else 0 end) as ss_item_qty
from DMA.re_item_day as re  join DMA.current_microcategories as cm using(Microcat_id)
                            join DMA.current_item as ci using(Item_id)
                            left join DMA.salesforce_usermapping as su using(User_id)
where 1 
and region='Москва' 
and logical_category in ('Realty.NewDevelopments', 'Realty.SecondarySell')
and event_date>='2019-01-01'
group by 1 
)
, base as 
(
select event_date
from prices_median_dev
union 
select event_date
from prices_median
union 
select event_date
from item_qty
)
select  b.event_date as ds,
        price_median,
        price_median_developer,
        nd_item_qty,
        nd_item_qty_developer,
        ss_item_qty
from base as b 
left join prices_median as pm using(event_date)
left join prices_median_dev as pmd using(event_date)
left join item_qty as iq using(event_date)
order by 1

    , case when 'Москва,Московская область' like '%'||cl.region||'%' then 'target'

    , count(distinct co.deliveryorder_id) as y

    and pay_date is not null
    and vertical = 'General'
group by 1,2

custom_sql:

        else city end) as region

where EventDate::date >= '20190101'
and (vertical = 'General'  or vertical = 'SpareParts')
and logical_category = 'General.Furniture'
and country = 'все регионы'
and (('Тюменская область,Красноярский край,Новосибирская область,Воронежская область,Костромская область,Амурская область,Брянская область,Ростовская область,Томская область,Еврейская АО,Архангельская область,Чувашия,Владимирская область,Белгородская область,Удмуртия,Оренбургская область,Мурманская область,Смоленская область,Ивановская область,Пермский край,Крым') like '%'||cl.region||'%'
    or ('Киров,,Уфа,Улан-Удэ,Комсомольск-на-Амуре') like '%'||cl.City||'%' )
and item_id not in (select item_id from dma.current_item where isDead)
group by 1,2
order by 1,2

custom_sql:
select 
    event_date::date as ds, 
    'target' as region,
    sum(metric_value) as y 
FROM dma.regional_ab_metrics
where 1=1 
    and user_segment_market = 'any'
    and is_user_asd = 'any'
    and event_date >= date_trunc('year', timestampadd(year,-3, current_timestamp))::date
    and logical_category_id in ('1393250007', '1393250008', '25176500001') 
    and metric_name = 'item_view'
group by 1, 2
order by 1, 2
